name: There They Are!
Lore: 'When unexplained droid losses are detected, a Droid Control Ship can call in reinforcements in seconds.',
Text: 'If a battle was just initiated, your non-unique battle druids are each power +1 for remainder of battle. (Immune to Sense if battle at a Naboo site.) OR Take a non-unique battle droid or non-unique droid starfighter into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',
